00:31:54,367 --> 00:31:58,248
However, when I play the game, this is all that I see.

611
00:31:58,248 --> 00:32:01,069
Today I'm gonna be talking about a mental flaw that I have,

612
00:32:01,069 --> 00:32:02,930
which I will be calling min-maxing.

