00:32:19,495 --> 00:32:23,118
I'm helpless against my need to reduce grinding and optimize my time.

620
00:32:23,118 --> 00:32:28,421
For me, the inclusion of this skill removed potential interesting play styles, made me

621
00:32:28,421 --> 00:32:32,804
feel guilty when I wanted to experiment, and in a general sense, slightly decreased my

622
00:32:32,804 --> 00:32:33,784
enjoyment of the game.

623
00:32:33,784 --> 00:32:38,647
What I'm calling min-maxing is pretty similar to other gaming neuroses.

624
00:32:38,647 --> 00:32:39,348
For example...

625
00:32:39,833 --> 00:32:42,014
needing to search every single hallway of a JRPG

