00:34:41,636 --> 00:34:44,577
Besides feeling like I'm forced to pick these options,

676
00:34:44,577 --> 00:34:46,658
they often end up decreasing the difficulty

677
00:34:46,658 --> 00:34:48,278
in the later stages of the game.

678
00:34:48,278 --> 00:34:50,379
