693
00:35:25,650 --> 00:35:27,731
and there's a heavy penalty for failure,

694
00:35:27,731 --> 00:35:29,852
such as losing an hour's progress,

695
00:35:29,852 --> 00:35:32,513
I feel like I'm disincentivized from trying anything new.

696
00:35:34,348 --> 00:35:36,969
To summarize, for people like me,

697
00:35:36,969 --> 00:35:39,149
