699
00:35:40,310 --> 00:35:42,170
but it can also feel like a curse

700
00:35:42,170 --> 00:35:44,571
that results in me having less choice as a player,

701
00:35:44,571 --> 00:35:48,212
taking fewer risks, and theoretically having less fun.

