00:36:02,684 --> 00:36:05,065
Try to prevent there being an optimal play style.

708
00:36:05,065 --> 00:36:06,545
If a single strategy works every time,

709
00:36:06,545 --> 00:36:08,986
there's no incentive for growth.

710
00:36:08,986 --> 00:36:10,326
Don't force the player to choose

711
00:36:10,326 --> 00:36:12,407
between fun and time efficiency.

